title: Johannis Gröningii Harmonia S.R. Tribunalis Wism. Cum Iudicio Aulico Et Camerali
creator: Gröning, Johann
subject: Historische Drucke
source: Gröning, Johann: Johannis Gröningii Harmonia S.R. Tribunalis Wism. Cum Iudicio Aulico Et Camerali  Qua trium horum Summorum Iudiciorum natura, Iurisdictionem fundandi modus, Procedendi ordo modernusve Stylus, succincte, nervose ac dilucide, delineantur, omniaque Novissimis Cameralibus Praeiudiciis illustrantur & corroborantur.
